1
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:41,160
You came so fast.

2
00:00:42,600 --> 00:00:43,530
It really is you.

3
00:00:44,760 --> 00:00:45,820
Too much nonsense.

4
00:00:50,560 --> 00:00:51,160
Sister Mu,

5
00:00:51,240 --> 00:00:52,120
don't be afraid.

6
00:00:52,120 --> 00:00:53,380
We are here to save you.

7
00:00:57,200 --> 00:00:57,760
Wuzhou.

8
00:00:58,720 --> 00:00:59,440
Wuzhou.

9
00:01:00,200 --> 00:01:01,240
Wuzhou.

10
00:01:03,800 --> 00:01:04,920
Wuzhou.

11
00:01:08,280 --> 00:01:09,000
Sister Mu.

12
00:01:10,440 --> 00:01:11,160
Lu Danyu,

13
00:01:12,440 --> 00:01:13,920
am I completely useless?

14
00:01:15,000 --> 00:01:16,530
How could you be, Sister Mu?

15
00:01:18,960 --> 00:01:21,160
Just by saying she knew him before I did,

16
00:01:21,520 --> 00:01:23,320
she tricked me into coming here.

17
00:01:23,960 --> 00:01:25,560
Why am I so stupid

18
00:01:26,200 --> 00:01:28,480
to be so easily swayed?

19
00:01:30,240 --> 00:01:31,000
Sister Mu.

20
00:01:31,680 --> 00:01:33,080
I don't even know

21
00:01:34,400 --> 00:01:37,039
when he lay down in this array.

22
00:01:38,160 --> 00:01:39,920
This is all my fault.

23
00:01:40,440 --> 00:01:41,880
He will be fine.

24
00:01:42,160 --> 00:01:43,880
He is the Child of the World.

25
00:01:44,440 --> 00:01:45,080
Sister Mu,

26
00:01:45,360 --> 00:01:46,620
it's not that serious.

27
00:01:47,880 --> 00:01:49,600
I know he cares for the world,

28
00:01:50,320 --> 00:01:52,450
has compassion for all living beings,

29
00:01:52,479 --> 00:01:54,240
and treats everyone well.

30
00:01:56,320 --> 00:01:58,320
I was used to him treating me well.

31
00:02:07,960 --> 00:02:09,220
I thought my whole life

32
00:02:09,240 --> 00:02:10,840
would just be like this.

33
00:02:11,400 --> 00:02:11,960
But...

34
00:02:12,680 --> 00:02:13,520
Why?

35
00:02:15,160 --> 00:02:18,240
Why lie in this array for me?

36
00:02:22,560 --> 00:02:23,760
Wei Wuzhou,

37
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:27,320
is this your so-called great love?

38
00:02:30,120 --> 00:02:30,760
Sister Mu,

39
00:02:31,079 --> 00:02:31,840
don't panic.

40
00:02:33,400 --> 00:02:34,260
Brother Wuzhou

41
00:02:34,280 --> 00:02:35,680
will definitely be fine.

42
00:02:51,240 --> 00:02:52,160
Lu Danyu,

43
00:02:52,600 --> 00:02:54,130
in that array over there...

44
00:02:56,320 --> 00:02:57,560
A magic array.

45
00:03:00,800 --> 00:03:01,480
Yiyi,

46
00:03:01,600 --> 00:03:02,930
did you find something?

47
00:03:05,440 --> 00:03:07,370
There's actually a person in here.

48
00:03:09,360 --> 00:03:10,760
What is going on?

49
00:03:11,800 --> 00:03:12,880
So that's how it is.

50
00:03:15,440 --> 00:03:16,680
How is it?

51
00:03:16,920 --> 00:03:18,850
He is the previous Son of the World.

52
00:03:21,720 --> 00:03:22,720
He is actually...

53
00:03:27,880 --> 00:03:28,880
In that case,

54
00:03:29,160 --> 00:03:30,600
aren't he and Brother Wuzhou

55
00:03:30,600 --> 00:03:32,860
blood brothers from different parents?

56
00:03:32,880 --> 00:03:33,440
But

57
00:03:33,640 --> 00:03:35,040
why is he lying here?

58
00:03:35,440 --> 00:03:36,720
Is he injured?

59
00:03:41,600 --> 00:03:42,400
Get lost.

60
00:03:44,360 --> 00:03:45,290
Don't touch him.

61
00:04:00,840 --> 00:04:01,560
Miss,

62
00:04:02,040 --> 00:04:03,300
are you in any trouble?

63
00:04:04,760 --> 00:04:05,280
Save me.

64
00:04:09,760 --> 00:04:10,220
Save me.

65
00:04:50,440 --> 00:04:51,700
The world is ruthless,

66
00:04:51,760 --> 00:04:53,800
and it's hard for demon cultivators.

67
00:04:53,800 --> 00:04:56,280
It is rare that you carry no hostility toward humans.

68
00:04:56,280 --> 00:04:58,610
It seems you have never taken a human life.

69
00:04:59,120 --> 00:04:59,800
In that case,

70
00:04:59,800 --> 00:05:01,200
you have nothing to fear.

71
00:05:01,840 --> 00:05:04,040
You may leave after your injuries heal.

72
00:05:23,000 --> 00:05:23,960
Smells so good.

73
00:05:25,880 --> 00:05:26,680
Yeah.

74
00:05:27,520 --> 00:05:29,250
Where is the smell coming from?

75
00:05:30,680 --> 00:05:31,280
It must be

76
00:05:31,400 --> 00:05:32,400
the new one.

77
00:05:32,720 --> 00:05:33,440
You mean

78
00:05:33,520 --> 00:05:34,600
the one the Taoist brought back?

79
00:05:34,600 --> 00:05:35,240
Shush.

80
00:05:49,640 --> 00:05:50,700
Thank you, Taoist.

81
00:05:51,280 --> 00:05:52,340
Thank you, Taoist.

82
00:05:57,440 --> 00:05:59,560
Look how sanctimonious he is.

83
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:01,800
Doing good deeds every day,

84
00:06:02,080 --> 00:06:04,140
helping us old, weak, and sick folks.

85
00:06:04,520 --> 00:06:05,560
Actually,

86
00:06:05,760 --> 00:06:08,320
he's secretly keeping a beautiful girl.

87
00:06:09,880 --> 00:06:10,360
I mean,

88
00:06:10,480 --> 00:06:12,140
what kind of nonsense is this?

89
00:06:13,280 --> 00:06:14,360
You worry too much.

90
00:06:14,520 --> 00:06:16,000
Just take what you're given.

91
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:17,130
Why are you nagging?

92
00:06:18,400 --> 00:06:20,000
I just can't stand it.

93
00:06:20,120 --> 00:06:20,760
Besides,

94
00:06:21,240 --> 00:06:22,700
everyone knows about him.

95
00:06:22,880 --> 00:06:24,280
Can't I say a few words?

96
00:06:25,120 --> 00:06:26,040
These days,

97
00:06:26,120 --> 00:06:27,800
even Taoists lack decency.

98
00:06:28,200 --> 00:06:29,880
If you think he lacks decency,

99
00:06:30,800 --> 00:06:33,360
how do you know if he's a real Taoist?

100
00:06:38,440 --> 00:06:39,280
Silly Taoist.

101
00:06:52,520 --> 00:06:54,000
Since your injuries are healed,

102
00:06:54,000 --> 00:06:55,600
you should leave on your own.

103
00:06:57,120 --> 00:06:58,380
Are you kicking me out?

104
00:07:00,600 --> 00:07:02,240
Humans and demons walk different paths.

105
00:07:02,240 --> 00:07:04,000
Besides, your injuries are healed,

106
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:05,530
so you should leave anyway.

107
00:07:05,760 --> 00:07:07,290
How is this kicking you out?

108
00:07:22,280 --> 00:07:22,760
Daoist.

109
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:28,450
Are there any demons roaming around here?

110
00:07:30,040 --> 00:07:31,440
Greetings, cultivator.

111
00:07:31,560 --> 00:07:32,290
Around here,

112
00:07:33,080 --> 00:07:35,140
there are no demons that harm humans.

113
00:07:41,600 --> 00:07:42,730
Sorry to bother you.

114
00:08:14,120 --> 00:08:15,050
Why are you back?

115
00:08:15,960 --> 00:08:17,420
Where did these come from?

116
00:08:17,640 --> 00:08:18,320
(Could it be

117
00:08:18,480 --> 00:08:19,680
that you stole them?)

118
00:08:19,800 --> 00:08:20,560
No.

119
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:21,720
I got these

120
00:08:21,920 --> 00:08:23,080
by gathering herbs on the mountain

121
00:08:23,080 --> 00:08:24,680
and trading them for silver.

122
00:08:24,960 --> 00:08:25,560
Also,

123
00:08:25,800 --> 00:08:27,400
don't think saying a few harsh words

124
00:08:27,400 --> 00:08:28,460
will make me leave.

125
00:08:28,760 --> 00:08:30,440
I know you're doing this for my own good.

126
00:08:30,440 --> 00:08:31,280
Is it because

127
00:08:31,360 --> 00:08:33,200
those demon-hunting cultivators came

128
00:08:33,200 --> 00:08:35,260
that you deliberately drove me away?

129
00:08:35,960 --> 00:08:37,289
Since you already know,

130
00:08:37,799 --> 00:08:39,000
why haven't you left?

131
00:08:39,480 --> 00:08:40,400
I'm not leaving.
